2003-09-18 15:50 UTC-0500 Paul Tucker <ptucker@sympatico.ca>
  * source/rtl/tget.prg
    * Check for !Empty(::type) @ 308 since Type can be NIL if no Picture.
    * This may not be the 'correct' fix, but solves the problem.

